TC-002	Chat Sharing	Verify that only authorized users can access the shared link	1. Generate a chat link.
2. Share it with an unauthorized user (someone without permission).
3. Attempt to open the link.	• Unauthorized users should see a message: "You do not have access to this chat."
• The system should prevent unauthorized viewing/editing.	High	Pass/Fail
TC-003	Chat Sharing	Verify that the chat link is accessible within the organization	1. Generate a chat link.
2. Share it with a colleague inside the organization.
3. Open the link from their system.	• The shared chat should open successfully.
• The recipient should be able to view the conversation.
• If edit permissions were granted, they should be able to send messages.
